   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-2" image="QN_SoceressTara.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk}<BR>We may still have a chance to turn this around. We must get the <FONT color=#a82424>Vision Orb</FONT> back before the <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT> lays hands on it.<BR>Ask <FONT color=#a82424>Sorceress Tara</FONT> where that <FONT color=#a82424>minotaur</FONT> lives. When you're ready, meet up with <FONT color=#a82424>Jake</FONT> at <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Hill</FONT> and proceed together. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n015_sorceress_tara-2" image="QM_MinotaurosNormal.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n015_sorceress_tara-2-a" mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>Is there a place where a minotaur might live in the vicinity of Mana Ridge?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Tara$<BR>I heard from Master Sorceress Cynthia.<BR>So a <FONT color=#a82424>minotaur</FONT> has taken the Vision Orb...?<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Minotaur</FONT>...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n015_sorceress_tara-2-a" image="QM_MinotaurosNormal.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n015_sorceress_tara-2-b" mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>I see. I understand.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Tara$<BR>After the clerics of Mana Ridge left for <FONT color=#a82424>Saint Haven</FONT> long ago, <FONT color=#a82424>Umbaba</FONT> took over the empty <FONT color=#a82424>Silent Monestery</FONT>. That's the only <FONT color=#a82424>minotaur</FONT> around Mana Ridge.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n015_sorceress_tara-2-b" image="QM_MinotaurosNormal.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n015_sorceress_tara-3" mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>Thank you for the advice.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Tara$<BR>Look, <FONT color=#a82424>Umbaba</FONT> is a large, powerful monster. Way bigger than what you're used to. When <FONT color=#a82424>Umbaba</FONT> attacks, it's hard to stop.<BR>Either hit it with an extra powerful skill to stop its advance, or dodge and counterattack.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n015_sorceress_tara-3" image="QM_MinotaurosNormal.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Tara$<BR>Well...you're our best chance to get the <FONT color=#a82424>Vision Orb</FONT> back from <FONT color=#a82424>Umbaba</FONT>.<BR>I know Master Sorceress Cynthia blames you, but… I trust you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n014_cleric_cedric-4" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n014_cleric_cedric-4-a" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>How are you feeling?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Cedric$<BR>Ah, may the Goddess's blessings be with you!<BR>It's an honor to meet you properly. You are the <FONT color=#a82424>savior</FONT> who rescued me. I wanted to thank you sooner, but with all the chaos... I'm really sorry...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n014_cleric_cedric-4-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n014_cleric_cedric-4-b" mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>I came to see Cleric Jake.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Cedric$<BR>Other than my injured leg that limits my movements, I'm fine. <BR>What brings you here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n014_cleric_cedric-4-b" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n014_cleric_cedric-5" mid="70"><![CDATA[<html>Not at all. I'll come see him later.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Cedric$<BR>Ahh... <FONT color=#a82424>Cleric Jake</FONT> is not here at the moment....<BR>I'm not sure where he went. Is it something urgent?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n014_cleric_cedric-5" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Cedric$<BR>Very well.<BR>May the Goddess's blessings be with you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
